<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10613434>
    dc:description "Fig. 10. Ero natashae sp. nov. A–C, E–F. Holotype, ♂ (BE_RMCA_ARA.Ara.129326). D. Paratype, ♀ (BE_RMCA_ARA.Ara.133379). A. Habitus, dorsal view. B. Habitus, lateral view. C. Habitus, posterior view. D. Habitus, lateral view. E. Palp, anterior view. F. Palp, showing the detail of cymbial basolateral extensions, retro-ventral view. Abbreviations: see Material and methods. Scale bars: A–B, D = 1 mm; C = 0.5 mm; E–F = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10613434/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10613436>
    dc:description "Fig. 11. Ero natashae sp. nov., holotype, ♂ (BE_RMCA_ARA.Ara.129326), palp. A. Prolateral view. B. Idem, slightly dorsal. C. Dorsal view. D. Retrolateral view. E. Idem, slightly ventral. F. Ventral view. Scale bars = 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10613436/files/figure.png" ;
