<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10613438>
    dc:description "Fig. 12. Ero natashae sp. nov., paratype, ♀ (BE_RMCA_ARA.Ara.133379), genitalia. A. Epigyne, ventral view. B. Idem, anterior view. C. Vulva, dorsal view. D. Idem, slightly lateral. Abbreviations: see Material and methods. Scale bars = 0.1 mm." ;
