    dc:description "Fig. 13. Ero natashae sp. nov., genitalia illustrations. A. Holotype, ♂ (BE_RMCA_ARA.Ara.129326), palp, retrolateral view. B. Idem, ventral view. C. Paratype, ♀ (BE_RMCA_ARA.Ara.133379), epigyne, ventral view. D. Vulva, dorsal view. Abbreviations: see Material and methods. Scale bars: A–B = 0.2 mm; C–D = 0.1 mm." ;
